1-1 Features
Feature: User Registration
	As a first-time clinic patient
	So that I can have a user profile on Espolea
	I want to create a profile

Feature: Log In
	As a returning clinic patient
	So that the site can track my registration and reviews
	I want to log in

Feature: Display the profile after 
	As a returning clinic patient
	So that I can see a history of past visits and reviews
	I want to display my profile after my login

Feature: Create a Clinic
	As an administrator
	So that users can review and register for a clinic
	I want to create a clinic

Feature: View list of all Clinics
	As any user
	So that I know what clinics I can visit
	I want to see a list of all the clinics

Feature: View a Particular Clinic
	As any user
	So that I can submit reviews and register for a clinic
	I want to view the details of a particular clinic